<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WishMeWell Apartment - Terms and Conditions</title>
    <style>
        /* General styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #c19b76;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        header img {
            max-height: 50px;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 10px;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
        }

        main {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #c19b76;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        li, p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .note {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #555;
        }

        /* Responsive styles */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                padding: 15px;
            }

            main {
                padding: 10px;
                margin: 10px;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

            li, p {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }

            header img {
                max-height: 40px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            header {
                font-size: 1rem;
                padding: 10px;
            }

            main {
                padding: 8px;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            li, p {
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }

            header img {
                max-height: 30px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <!-- Logo Placeholder -->
        <img src="/images/favicon.png" alt="WishMeWell Apartment Logo">
        WishMeWell Apartment - Terms and Conditions
    </header>

    <main>
        <h2>Check-In and Check-Out</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Check-In Time:</strong> 2:00 PM</li>
            <li><strong>Check-Out Time:</strong> 12:00 PM</li>
            <li>Note: Guests checking out after 12:00 PM will be charged ₦10,000 for every additional hour.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Smoking and Pets</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Smoking is strictly prohibited inside the apartment and within the premises.</li>
            <li>Pets are not allowed inside the apartment or within the premises.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Payment and Refunds</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>All payments, whether made online or at the apartment, are <strong>non-refundable</strong>.</li>
            <li>Guests can extend their reservation dates by providing a 72-hour notice to avoid overbooking.</li>
            <li>If an inquiry was made before making payment on the same day, guests must confirm availability again before payment to avoid overbooking. Refunds will not be issued in cases of overbooking.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Guest Policy</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Maximum number of guests for a <strong>normal stay: 1 Bed</strong> 3 - 4 <strong>#60,000</strong></li>
            <li>Maximum number of guests for a <strong>normal stay: 2 Bed</strong> 5 - 6 <strong>#80,000</strong></li>
            <li>Maximum number of guests for a <strong>Get Together: 1 Bed</strong> 5 - 6 persons #100,000</li>
            <li>Maximum number of guests for a <strong>Get Together: 2 Bed</strong> 10 - 12 persons #120,000</li>
        </ul> 

        <h2>Damages</h2>
        <p>Any damages to the property will be taken seriously and evaluated for appropriate charges.</p>

        <h2>Room Cleaning</h2>
        <p>Rooms are cleaned every two days after check-in.</p>

        <h2>Caution Fee</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>A refundable caution fee of ₦50,000 is required.</li>
            <!-- <li><strong>Refund via Bank Transfer or POS:</strong> Processing time is 2–3 working days.</li> -->
            <li><strong>Refund via Cash Payment:</strong> Refund will be given on the check-out day.</li>
            <li>Note: The apartment will be inspected before the caution fee is refunded to ensure there are no damages.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Music and Noise Policy</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Loud music is prohibited. DJs are not allowed.</li>
            <li>Guests may use Bluetooth speakers, but volume levels should remain reasonable.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Activity Restrictions</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>All activities must remain within the apartment.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Other Policies</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Guests are advised to double-check all personal belongings before leaving. The management will not be held responsible for any lost items.</li>
            <li>Keep noise levels reasonable to respect other guests and neighbors.</li>
            <li>Management reserves the right to terminate the stay without refund if these policies are violated.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="note">By staying at WishMeWell Apartment, you agree to abide by these terms and conditions. Failure to comply may result in additional charges or termination of your stay without refund.</p>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
